Please note that this contract depends on the ERC20 token standard for the `withdrawForeignTokens` function. The provided address `0x239C09c910ea910994B320ebdC6bB159E71d0b30` is used for the transfer function. Also, please review the contract carefully and test it thoroughly before deploying it to the mainnet.
